# Changelog

## 2.0

  + Add support for multiple PPTX files in one invocation
  + Refactor code to deduplicate URLs across all files; check each URL once
  + Add threading support for a big performance boost
  + Instead of displaying results to the screen, generate a CSV report

## 1.2

  + Removed dependency on python-pptx, adding code to parse slide bullets
  + Updated User-Agent to modern Chrome on macOS
  + Change request to GET from HEAD (more overhead, but more reliable server
    responses)
  + Change timeout to 1 request over 10 seconds

